E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('776','268','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" style=\\\\\"width: 441px; height: 366px\\\\\" src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2011/0621/20110621052623803.jpg\\\\\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">为加大全国文明卫生县城创建力度，进一步改善城区环境卫生和交通秩序，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">21</span><span style=\\\\\"mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，嘉鱼县创建办组织城管执法大队、市场中心、交警、茶庵社区等相关部门，对城区脏乱差等现象开展突击检查，并进行了综合治理。</span></span></span><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">在茶庵农贸市场、烟墩路、方庄菜市场等地，记者看到，不少经营肉、鱼、菜和水果的游商游贩不进市场内经营，而是推着板车、三轮车就地叫卖，在机动车道上摆摊设点，致使过往交通拥堵不堪；部分商店的货物摆出门外出店经营，影响到市民正常通行和店面整洁美观。</span></span></span><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">联合执法人员对商贩们进行了耐心劝导，并指定了合法经营范围，教育经营户守法经营、游商游贩集中归市，引导其增强创建全国文明卫生县城的大局意识和责任感，自觉参与到全县创建活动中来。</span></span></span><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">为了营造街净路畅、树青草绿、灯亮墙美的良好城市环境，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2005</span><span style=\\\\\"mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年来我县开展了三次&ldquo;省级文明县城&rdquo;活动，也连续蝉联荣誉称号。此次嘉鱼县作为咸宁市唯一县市、全省</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span><span style=\\\\\"mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个县市之一参加全国文明卫生县城候评，创建工作成为当前一项重中之重的中心工作。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('778','268','县创建办','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">按照县创建指挥部《关于印发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&lt;</span>嘉鱼县创建全国文明卫生县城实施方案<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&gt;</span>的通知》（嘉创指<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2011]4</span>号）文件的要求，县创建办于<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>日至<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>日对交通局、商务局、工商局、水利局、文体新局、卫生局、城市规划执法局、公安局、鱼岳镇<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>家职能单位履行职能工作情况进行了检查。现将有关情况通报如下：</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">一、交通局：一是运管所配合联合执法队对城区车辆运输、停靠秩序进行了整治；二是对三湖连江游船停靠码头选址进行了调研；三是对城区公交站牌损坏污染问题进行了摸底和保洁，目前已维修<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>个，计划新增<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>个；四是城区所有公交车辆和出租车辆制作发布了文明创建公益广告标语。</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">存在问题：一是城区通村客车进站不规范，沿街抛洒垃圾；二是城区非法营运黑车仍然存在。</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">二、商务局：一是投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>多万元对鱼岳市场进行了大幅度改造；二是茶庵市场正在进行规划设计，即将整修；三是对城区各市场下水道进行疏通，维修顶棚堵漏；四是协助联合执法队重点整治市场周边经营秩序；五是投入<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1.5</span>万元解决了茶庵市场垃圾清运问题，建立了地埋式垃圾箱一个。</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">存在问题：一是资金缺乏，鱼岳市场顶棚还未得到彻底整修，存在安全隐患；二是市场熟食店未能使用防蝇纱罩；三是市场内卫生清扫不及时，频次不高。</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">三、工商局：一是印制文明创建宣传单<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8000</span>余份，分发到城区各经营门店；二是参与联合执法队对城区经营门店占道经营现象进行整治；三是取缔食品无证经营户<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">370</span>余户；四是组织工商执法人员稽查城区食品无证生产销售经营门店；五是取缔了商标广告不规范行为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>家；六是制订了《百城万家无假货集中清查整治活动方案》。</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">存在问题：一是城区许多早点摊点为无证经营没有查处；二农贸市场熟食店员防蝇罩基本未使用。</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">四、水利局：一是分配任务，组织专班人员每星期对三湖连江漂浮物进行打捞；二是安排所属主管部门对西门堤水果市场进行了管理。</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">存在问题：一是四邑公堤两侧、西门堤市场及主副坝路的垃圾较多；二是梅屎桥下到鱼岳高中转角有漂浮垃圾。</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">五、文体新局：存在问题：一是没有创建方案和工作专班；二是图书馆、文化馆等公共场所无禁烟标识。</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">六、卫生局：一是按照要求将创建任务细化分解到所属单位，安排专班人员落实；二是开展了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>次食品安全监督检查。</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">存在问题：一是少数餐饮单位卫生状况较差，门口污渍油烟较多；二是理发店等公共场所服务人员体检率不高。</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">七、城市规划执法局：一是环卫所加大了对城区清扫和清运，重点是人行旁、工业园区、大崇山路、西门堤等地段卫生死角；二是洒水车每天<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>次对城区主次干道进行冲洗；三是清除了二乔公园对面和法院旁的建筑垃圾，平整了土堆；四是对城区流动摊点进行了整治，落实了&ldquo;五安家&rdquo;活动；五是组织联合执法队整治出店经营户<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">814</span>户、早点夜市摊点<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">187</span>个；六是剪修城区主次干道绿化树（带）。</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">存在问题：一是城区&ldquo;五乱&rdquo;现象比较突出；二是运土（渣）车辆夜间作业，沿街抛洒，重点是发展大道和沿湖大道魏家塘段；三是东岳路、鱼岳路口、西正街口、聚丰宾馆等处早点、夜市摊点仍有占道经营现象；四是城区所有垃圾屋铁门全部丢失，未恢复；五是沿街乱拉横幅、乱安装广告牌现象较突出；六是主干道上摩托车、电器修理店仍然占道作业。</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">八、公安局：一是联合城管、交通等部门对城区运输车辆、正三轮车入城等违规行为进行打击，并对一暴力抗法三轮车主进行了刑拘；二是整治城区出租车乱停靠、乱掉头现象；三是对盗窃丽红超市交通路口遮阳棚者进行了刑拘。</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">存在问题：一是个别工地运土车夜间作业没有及时查处，沿街抛洒，特别是发展大道和魏家塘工地；二是石油公司门口铲土车屡禁不止；三是城区摩的非法载客现象仍然存在；四是部分人行横道信号灯未安装。</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">九、鱼岳镇：一是各社区由第一书记召开了创建工作动员会议，落实了专班专人，制定了措施方案；二是各社区与所辖&ldquo;门前四包&rdquo;单位签订了合同书；三是各社区利用市民学校开展宣传教育；四是组织社区志愿者对支街小巷进行了清扫；五是西街社区组织老年艺术团开展了一次大型文体演出活动；六是投入<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5000</span>元，落实了城区公共旱厕水费问题；七是组织西街社区、陆码头村、南门湖村<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>条船只及<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>多名劳力，用<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>天时间对陆码河水上漂浮物进行了打涝。</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\">存在问题：一是交通协管员还未落实到位；二是支街小巷&ldquo;牛皮癣&rdquo;比较突出；三是新建围墙还未动工；四是城区旱厕未冲洗和清扫。</span></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></span></o:p></span></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>');");
